        <a href='/about/' class='text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground'>소개</a>
        <a href='/privacy/' class='text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground'
            >개인정보처리 안내</a
        >
        <a href='/contact/' class='text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground'>문의</a>
